<p style=3D"text-align: left;">Professor Jayant Baliga, who&nbsp;will be th=
e Chief Guest at our Convocation will deliver a lecture (details below) on
</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">Thursday the 21st July 2016 at ICSR Auditori=
um at 15.00 h.</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br>
</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">All are invited to attend.</p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br>
